SNAPCAT
=======

Combine directory tree, file contents (cat), and SHA256 hashes into a single
JSON or Markdown document.  Snapcat walks a directory tree, respects ignore
rules, reads file contents, computes cryptographic hashes, and outputs a
structured report – perfect for snapshots, code reviews, or feeding data to
LLMs.

Version: 0.1.0
License: GPL-3.0
Repository: https://github.com/mroczect/snapcat   (placeholder)


